Task Engine

The task engine has three structural layers.

Templates

Reusable checklist definitions.

Tables:

task_templates
task_template_sections
task_template_items

Templates define structure but do not represent real work.

Assignments

Scheduled tasks.

Table:

task_assignments

Assignments define:

date

template reference

title

display mode

Instances

Actual execution records.

Tables:

task_assignment_instances
task_assignment_instance_targets
task_item_logs

Instances represent tasks that exist on a specific day.

Ad-Hoc Tasks

Custom tasks create a simplified parent structure:

task_assignments
task_assignment_instances
task_assignment_instance_targets

The instance cannot exist without a parent assignment.

